stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PENDING
    PENDING --> PAID: payment success
    PAID --> SHIPMENT_CREATED: shipment booked
    SHIPMENT_CREATED --> PICKED_UP: provider update
    PICKED_UP --> IN_TRANSIT: provider update
    IN_TRANSIT --> OUT_FOR_DELIVERY: provider update
    OUT_FOR_DELIVERY --> DELIVERED: provider update
    DELIVERED --> COMPLETED: close order
    SHIPMENT_CREATED --> FAILED: booking failed
    FAILED --> RETURNED: return initiated
    RETURNED --> REFUNDED: refund processed
